info:
  title: Example of HTML forms
  version: 1.0.0

    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/x-www-urlencoded-form:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                street:
                  type: string
                city:
                  type: string
                province:
                  type: string
                country:
                  type: string
                postcode:
                  type: string
                tags:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Great Success!
